# A&P Study Buddy

A React-based study tool powered by OpenAI's Responses API.

## üöÄ Features
- AI‚Äëdriven explanations
- Quizzes
- Image labeling
- Clinical case questions
- Flashcards
- Vision support for diagrams

## üì¶ Install
```
npm install
```

## ‚ñ∂Ô∏è Run
```
